name: Bauble: Card
description:
A stylised christmas bauble featuring a geometric pattern. Tags are hand stamped with a custom designed rubber stamp. Choose from either kraft or white heavy weight paper. Alternate paper/ ink colour options shown.  

A6 size (105mm x 148mm when folded) 
Paper options: Heavy weight recycled kraft paper (270gsm) OR heavy weight smooth white paper (280gsm)
Stamp design is custom made 
Blank Interior  
Packaged in cellophane pack with envelope
